[snickers]

262
00:17:25,962 --> 00:17:27,296
How much longer?

263
00:17:27,380 --> 00:17:28,631
[Ray] Moments.

264
00:17:28,714 --> 00:17:30,466
We have shocked
and amplified the tissue sample

265
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:32,176
to replicate the life span of the…

266
00:17:33,135 --> 00:17:34,929
-The what?
-Well, I don't see much point

267
