284
00:18:37,074 --> 00:18:38,326
What about my life?

285
00:18:38,951 --> 00:18:41,871
What happens to me in 855 days?

286
00:18:41,954 --> 00:18:43,122
[chokes, coughs]

287
00:18:43,205 --> 00:18:44,665
Jefferson!

288
00:18:45,791 --> 00:18:47,668
