and destroy the world.

303
00:19:42,890 --> 00:19:44,850
He did what needed to be done.

304
00:19:44,934 --> 00:19:47,520
Science must move forward.

305
00:19:49,146 --> 00:19:53,192
Great things do not come
without risk, cost.

306
