My heart. I do love them.
Probably too much.

419
00:27:02,913 --> 00:27:04,832
Yeah, they're better than people.
That's what I always say.

420
00:27:04,915 --> 00:27:06,416
[Jen] Right? Drives me up the fucking wall

421
